Hi Nepotu,

It;s been great exchanging messages so please accept my deepest gratitude for your great work on ALL football games.

I look forward to end of the season in NCAA & NFL as well as the Bowl games & NFL championship. Whatever you will have available for DL will be great.

I leave tomoro & so take care & I will be back in Dec.

All the best to a Class Act on TPB !!!

Also deep gratitude to the rippers. They do the hardest work.
Thank you, my friend! I hope too see you soon (well..., in dec). God bless you and enjoy your trip!
